    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Biofuel stoves that burn biomass solid fuel in pellet form to generate heat. Examples of biomass solid fuel include: corn kernels, wood pellets, and cherry pits. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
